{"word":"χάρισμα","slug":"χάρισμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>χάρισμα, ατος, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χαρίζομαι\">χαρίζομαι</a></el>] ‘that which results from the activity of generosity’, in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> always in connection with divine generosity bestowed on believers, <b>divine gift<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in general <b><a href='B:520 1:11'>Ro 1:11</a>; <a href='B:520 5:15'>5:15f</a>; <a href='B:520 6:23'>6:23</a>; <a href='B:520 11:29'>11:29</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to corporate welfare <b><a href='B:520 12:6'>Ro 12:6</a>; <a href='B:530 1:7'>1 Cor 1:7</a>; <a href='B:530 7:7'>7:7</a>; <a href='B:530 12:4'>12:4</a>, <a href='B:530 12:9'>9</a>, <a href='B:530 12:28'>28</a>, <a href='B:530 12:30'>30f</a>; <a href='B:540 1:11'>2 Cor 1:11</a>; <a href='B:610 4:14'>1 Ti 4:14</a>; <a href='B:620 1:6'>2 Ti 1:6</a>; <a href='B:670 4:10'>1 Pt 4:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:χάρις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:χαριτόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}